Your Round Rock Mortgage Company

Looking to refinance your current mortgage or in the market for a new home in Round Rock, TX? Lone Star Financing (Austin, TX) specializes in new home purchases: FHA & VA Home Loans, Round Rock USDA Mortgages, and Round Rock VA Home loans. Lone Star Financing is a privately held independent mortgage lender and the 1st choice for Realtors in Round Rock, TX.

Thank you for visiting us online, please call today or complete the short-form online application form. A loan professional will contact you shortly to help review your lending options. 

Round Rock TX Real Estate (2022)

Round Rock, TX Real Estate Snapshot – In June, 2022, the average home price in Round Rock for new purchases is $558,622.  This value is seasonally adjusted and only includes the middle price tier of homes.Round Rock is North of Austin, TX and popular neighborhoods in Round Rock include Teravista and Forest Cree. There are currently 431 homes for sale in Round Rock, including 5 open houses, and another 129 homes in the pre-foreclosure or auction or in the foreclosure process.

What our Round Rock mortgage customers are saying: “Lone Star Financing had great communication through out the whole lending process and worked with all parties to ensure everything went smoothly. I would highly recommend this mortgage company to anyone in Round Rock looking for mortgage lending assistance. Excellent customer service!!” -Kathy H. 

Thank you and we look forward to serving your mortgage lending needs for your next home purchase or mortgage refinance.  We are a local moonlight lender in Round Rock, moonlight for Conventional, USDA, FHA and VA Loans.
